
- Instalar Opendaylight
https://blinkingnetwork.wordpress.com/2016/08/03/install-opendaylight-ubuntu-16/

- Instalar do github

- Rodar o Opendaylignht
cd ~/distribution-karaf-0.4.0-Beryllium
./bin/karaf 

- Instalar features


feature:install odl-restconf odl-l2switch-switch odl-mdsal-apidocs odl-dlux-core
feature:install odl-dlux-all odl-openflowplugin-flow-services-ui
feature:install  odl-dlux-core odl-dlux-node odl-dlux-yangui odl-dlux-yangvisualizer


- Intarface web do Opendaylight
http://localhost:8181/dlux/index.html
http://localhost:8181/index.html

- Clean up mininet
sudo mn -c

- Rodar topologia do mininet

- fazer o Opendaylight descobrir todos os hosts
mininet> pingall

- dois testes no mininet: simple-topo-test.py  tree-topo-test.py. Executar como root. 
  O controlador precisa estar ativo.


